<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This message is used to send goals from one application to another (e.g., a point of care system to a clinical repository). Many of the segments associated with this event are optional. This optionality allows systems in need of this information to set up transactions that fulfill their requirements.</p>
</div>
